title: Kylie Jenner Is Moving Her Birthday, Apparently
text:
Kylie Jenner Is Moving Her Birthday, Apparently 
Her calendar printed a weird mistake. Most Popular By Kristina Rodulfo Jan 4, 2017 Because 2016 was the year of " like, realizing stuff ," one mistake on Kylie Jenner's 2017 calendar did not go unnoticed by fans. In August, her birthday is marked on the 20th, but her actual birthday is the 10th. Some people who have the calendar tweeted about it in December, but more are noticing the odd mix-up just now. It's unclear whether there is a misprint on just a few calendars or all of them.   @KylieJenner we share the same birthday of august 10th but your calendar says august 20th... #stillcutedoe pic.twitter.com/Rbao22soHz
